Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You timed it well to scatter\Nthe three to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have practiced quite a bit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it is a pretty complicated song...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you\Nimmediately understand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm manipulating\Nthese guys with my flute
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you understood\Nhow difficult this song is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pretty impressive punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't completely\Nunderstand this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,True... Since art is so foreign to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But since she uses that flute\Nto manipulate,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it means that song must contain\Nindividually specific sound patterns
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to control each and every movement\Nof those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty confident when it comes\Nto just analyzing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but this time it's not looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand\Nmusical notes whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:56.19,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(458,275)}Fakeout! Shikamaru gambles in order to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fakeout! Shikamaru gambles in order to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll specially show you\Nthe Camellia Dance next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say things\Nyou can't even do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This bone is harder than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have a taste of it\Nwith your own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one that's heard\Nthis song and lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Finale, Ninth Passage,\NDemon Revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The melody's changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's gonna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The speed at which he flees\Nafter determining
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that these Material Ghosts\Nare dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've used my precious Paper Bombs\Nand Smoke Bombs all at once
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and all I could do was hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That white one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,bit off my physical energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing that shuriken passed through,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that thing is semi-materialistic\Nwith very little mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Chakra itself with an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably Chakra that's shaped\Nmostly by mental energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it seeks stability\Nand craves for physical energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I continue dealing with\Nthose "Hungry Chakra "
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to build up my Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Shinobi who can\Nmake special Chakra like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's without a doubt, a Secret Ninjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means I should leave\Nthe white thing alone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and aim for the main body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The quickest way would be\Nto stop the sound of the flute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be impossible to get close to\Nthat woman in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing would be to capture\Nthose three with Shadow Possession Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's difficult too since they're\Nattacking me separately at different times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let even one escape\NI'd be attacked and it'd be the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any openings in\Neither offense or defense this woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! She might be\Na pretty good Shogi player.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My remaining Ninja tools\Nare twelve kunai knives,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,nine shuriken, twelve meters of wire,\None Flash Bomb and one Paper Bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm playing without\Nrooks or bishops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I lose them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's not possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Eat this, Akamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't eat you won't\Nget your strength back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Akamaru, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the issue of those guys too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance of the Camellia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you can predict\Nthese guys' movements
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nowhere you can run, little rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find you and break you\Ninto pieces right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Everything's ready.\NAll that remains is to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be nine attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The outcome will be decided\Nduring the attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wishful thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jutsu manipulated by\Nthis sound is invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever plans you have\Nto win against me... is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Scampering around, you little rat!\NWhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a cheap trick.\NYou think you can make a fool of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Five... six...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,seven... eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Scurrying around to get away.\NWhat is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lengthened the shadows\Nwith light and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Possession Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Possession Jutsu...\Na success!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How were you able to predict\Nthese guys' movements?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could have heard\Nthe differences in my music patterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't listening to\Nthe sounds at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something other\Nthan the sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that give away your command patterns,\Nisn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The movement of the three...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you memorized\Nmy finger movements and predicted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that's possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your right index finger\Nand ring finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound that you make\Nwith those
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,along with the left middle finger\Nand pinkie,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that middle crab pincher man\Nstands ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your right thumb and index finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and your left index finger and pinkie,\Nthe club man charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,While you were dodging my attacks\Nand looking for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was observing each and every one\Nof your finger moves in detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,analyzing and memorizing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're bound by\NShadow Possession Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The most interesting rule\Nof the Shogi play is that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you can use pieces you obtain\Nas your own pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on out...\Nit's my turn to attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'll hunt you down\Nusing the three pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking pretty composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand ready with a kunai knife\Nat least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My weapon is just this flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that there hasn't been a person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who's heard the sound of\Nthis flute and lived, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad you aren't able to\Nuse the pieces, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Next it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Possession Jutsu,\Nsuccessful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'd hunt you down\Nusing the pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I used the three pieces as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In attacking, the first hand\Nis the trick, a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The basics are to score\Nwith the second hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this\NI'll need to force out with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that I'd get to\Nsecond state in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It ticks me off but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll acknowledge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy was a pretty impressive scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true you're somewhat sharp, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't go as\Nyou've planned from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she gonna force herself out\Nof the Shadow Possession Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that tremendous Chakra?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jutsu's gonna come loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be worrying about\Nsaving Chakra anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way\Nbut to use that Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Art: Shadow Strangle Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he grabbing my body\Nwith the shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as if I'm being grabbed\Nby a real hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But, no more than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! What an incredible strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At this distance\NI'll lose to that strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon Flute: Chains of Fantasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a... Genjutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you aiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,While in second stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I manipulate many Genjutsu\Nwith my flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of those, this one is\Nan appropriate for that little rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This Genjutsu stops the movement\Nof the prey and ties it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? How's it feel to\Nbe the one tied up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was your last move huh?\NUnfortunately, it's a return checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Little rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke his own finger\Nwith his own shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he release the Genjutsu\Nwith that pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he kept pretending to\Nbe bound by the Jutsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you this already
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that the first hand is the trick,\Na fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The basics are to score\Nwith the second move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover this second move...\Nit's a little different from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Shadow Strangle Jutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the closer in distance you are\Nto the subject the stronger the hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I carelessly got too close...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The most careless thing was\Nthe words you said earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"my weapon is just the flute."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking pretty composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand ready with a kunai knife at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My weapon is just this flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that\Nthere hasn't been a person
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who's heard the sound of this flute\Nand lived, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I threw the kunai knife\Nright in front of you and missed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,was to lead you to pick it up\Nand come closer to me, you see?
Comment: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:06.46,ED8,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.76,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:17.85,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:20.39,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:23.19,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:28.83,ED8,,0,0,0,,Would you think it was\Na bother if I approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:34.24,ED8,,0,0,0,,Despite my doubts,\NI worked up my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:40.17,ED8,,0,0,0,,My clumsy attempts with words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:45.84,ED8,,0,0,0,,You listened without turning away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:51.96,ED8,,0,0,0,,No wonder I get carried away by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:59.03,ED8,,0,0,0,,But you don't feel anything for me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:02.23,ED8,,0,0,0,,I feel so sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.20,ED8,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:05.67,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:08.71,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:11.44,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:14.51,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:17.02,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:20.22,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:22.76,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:25.73,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:30.36,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Comment: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:36.43,ED8,,0,0,0,,ED End
